ake It with You (TV series)|Make It with You]]'' due to the quarantine caused by the [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the Philippines|2019-20 Wuhan coronavirus pandemic]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.abs-cbn.com/entertainment/03/14/20/read-abs-cbn-statement-on-special-primetime-programming-amid-metro-manila-quarantine|title=READ: ABS-CBN statement on special primetime programming amid Metro Manila quarantine|publisher=[[ABS-CBN News]]|date=March 14, 2020|accessdate=March 29, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==International broadcast==\n* {{flagicon|Kenya}} [[Kenya]] \u2013 [[NTV (Kenya)|NTV]] <small>(December 18, 2017 - April 7, 2018)</small>\n* {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Indonesia]] \u2013 [[MNCTV]] <small>(November 21, 2016 - January 22, 2017)</small><ref>[http://www.duniatv.net/2016/11/on-wings-of-love-pernikahan-palsu-demi.html \"On The Wings of Love\", Pernikahan Palsu demi Dapatkan Status Kewarganegaraan (Plus Jadwal Tayang di MNCTV!)]</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Thailand}} [[Thailand]] \u2013 [[Channel 3 (Thailand)|Channel 3]] <small>(March 6, 2017 - June 20, 2017)</small><ref>[http://www.thaitv3.com/%E0%B8%8B%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%AA%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%8A%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%873/series/243/%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B8%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A2---%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%A7%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%88%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%81-.html \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e27\u0e38\u0e48\u0e19\u0e27\u0e32\u0e22...\u0e2b\u0e31\u0e27\u0e43\u0e08\u0e15\u0e34\u0e14\u0e1b\u0e35\u0e01 (On the Wings of Love)] at [[Channel 3 (Thailand)|thaitv3.com]]</ref>\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of telenovelas of ABS-CBN]]\n* [[List of programs broadcast by Jeepney TV]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{official website|http://onthewingsoflove.abs-cbn.com/ On the Wings of Love's official website}}\n*[http://otwolista.com Fan Page]\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KcvuVKA6H9c/ Official trailer]\n*{{IMDb title|tt5513960}}\n\n{{ABS-C